                     <interp inst="t18410823-2182-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18410823-2182-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp> for stealing, on the 18th <hi rend="italic">of</hi> August, 1 wheelbarrow, value 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18410823-name-1119" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18410823-name-1119" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
